I’m excited to share my latest collaboration with @roseshireco , featuring a stunning floral collection. This collaboration truly reflects my personal style, combining florals, travel, and showcasing my favorite place where I feel most authentic.

I had the pleasure of working closely with the Roseshire team to create a unique collaboration that captures the essence of Mexico’s hidden gems. From designing the interior and exterior to carefully selecting the florals, we aimed to present a beautiful representation of these remarkable places.

Experience the vibrant energy of summer as Destino Paraíso transforms your surroundings into a paradise of pure bliss. I sincerely hope you adore this collaboration as much as I do!

Send this beautiful floral bouquet to your travel bestie or someone special in your life .💐🧡✈️

xx
